VekBase/
├─ app/
│  ├─ analytics/        # metrics.py (REALIZED Metrics, optional unrealized via mark_prices)
│  ├─ core/             # trade_model, trade_repo, retrieval (Keyword Stub), decision_card, (Simulation uses sim/)
│  ├─ sim/              # simple_walk (deterministische Mini-Simulation + Persistenz)
│  └─ ui/               # console.py (Streamlit Konsole: Trades, Analytics, Simulation, DevTools)
├─ data/                # (lokal, nicht versioniert erwartet) trades.csv, results/, optional notes/, cache/
├─ docs/
│  ├─ CONTEXT/          # 10 Kontext-Dateien (Charter, Manifesto, Glossary, Schema, Decision Spec, RAG Policy, Test Strategy, UI Spec, Roadmap, Working Agreements)
│  └─ DOCUMENTATION/    # architecture, tmp_backlogCollection (Backlog Sammelstelle)
├─ tests/               # Pytest Module (trade_model, metrics, retrieval, sim, equity curve, etc.)
├─ README.md            # Kurzstart (lokal-first)
└─ requirements.txt     # Python Abhängigkeiten (leichtgewichtig)

Not Implemented Yet:
- Embeddings / RAG Retrieval Filter (ticker, as_of)
- DecisionCard vollständige Felder (action, risks, confidence)
- Unrealized Equity Curve / CAGR / Pattern Analytics
- Erweiterte Sim Parameter (TP/SL/Kosten)

Konventionen:
- Keine sys.path Hacks (pytest.ini steuert Pfad)
- Reine Berechnungen in analytics, Persistenz explizit in sim/simple_walk.run_and_persist
- Kontext-Sync: Roadmap = Quelle für offene Items; Charter/Test Strategy/UI Spec referenzieren nur
